#-------------- file header ---------------
4 bytes: Magic bytes (blockchain identifier: bitcoin,litecoin, etc)
4 bytes: Encodes size N of file

#-------------- block --------------- ( 80 Bytes)

4 Bytes: Version
32 Bytes : Last block hash
32 Bytes : Merkle root
4 Bytes :  timestamp
4 Bytes : difficulty target
4 Bytes : nonce

